name: Naruko (Sexy Jutsu Naruto)
description:
This is an SD 1.5 LoRA for Naruto using Sexy Jutsu. Example images were picked but not altered or improved from 512x768 txt2img results to give a realistic impression of what it looks like. Example images were generated using AOM3A1.

Training data leans heavily toward NSFW and questionable content, but can easily generate SFW as well.

The prompt "naruko \(naruto\)" should be enough to trigger the model.

Other useful prompts:
-"naruto" or "naruto uzumaki". These tags were pruned from training images, but most anime models know who Naruto is, so you're likely to get his clothes on generated images.

-"facial marks", "blue eyes", and "blond hair" help reinforce common character traits.

-"smoke" makes the smoke from the actual jutsu appear.
